{"tid":1515473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特狗政府追咗我三年稅想問唔交會點？","createTime":"2019-08-29T07:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T16:31:29.000Z","uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"43b6a9417db1dfaef063ae62cdf14cd292bdcd16","tid":1515473,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:13:51.000Z","msg":"有無人答到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac28d36fc285ae099b8f2e4bc85b426fd739aaa","tid":1515473,"uid":273916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:13:58.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3J6Zqr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3J6Zqr9.jpg&h=398279dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民陣電話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用於傳短訊</span></span>, 不建議致電<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTykUks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTykUks.jpg&h=e262c427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vD12Zp3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvD12Zp3.gif&h=f9a83f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GcUsmkJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGcUsmkJ.gif&h=2a4b8943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7Tdf8O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7Tdf8O.png&h=13ffde59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n831民陣大遊行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJLGv0x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJLGv0x.gif&h=e32fe2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZmfnY9d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZmfnY9d.gif&h=d6709f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n901 和你塞 13:00 <a href=\"http://見t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A6%8Bt.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=78ac6d31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">見t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=a2565ab6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每晚10點大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=5d7ea963\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1170684516349159%2Fposts%2F2398098013607797%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=997916f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102458676557543%2Fposts%2F1582783125191750%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=b9d97341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo</a><br />\n將窗嗌口號變成一種普及的生活方式，會好大感染力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyn9vh9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcyn9vh9.png&h=f1d434e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89367f0413f2e4773309deae152d11d7fd8d7115","tid":1515473,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"d0a24b52799fe9ff086050fb736272d305d36a0e","tid":1515473,"uid":273916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43b6a9417db1dfaef063ae62cdf14cd292bdcd16","tid":1515473,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:13:51.000Z","msg":"有無人答到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:16:23.000Z","msg":"細數不起訴 但要交罰款<br />\n<br />\n根據香港稅例，打工仔沒有依時把應課薪俸稅通知稅務局，或沒有依時呈交報稅表的話，一般不會收到起訴，但會收到罰款。但屢犯不改者，又或犯錯程度嚴重，則會收到檢控。<br />\n<br />\n比起逃稅，本地打工仔更常犯的錯誤是漏報或少報，這時候稅務局會根據違例次數評定罰款額，「違例」定義是指犯事人曾接警告信、以罰款代替檢控、被法庭罰款或收到第82A條的罰款評稅，具體如下：<br />\n<br />\n(a) 第一次違例：少徵收稅款的10%。<br />\n<br />\n(b) 5年內第二次違例：少徵收稅款的20%。<br />\n<br />\n(c) 5年內第三次違例或其後再犯：少徵收稅款的35%。<br />\nSource : 紅底01 <br />\n另外可參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/pol/ppo.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fpol%2Fppo.htm&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=f1788e3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/pol/ppo.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6b06447bc6f715938019473d28e0669262544567","tid":1515473,"uid":74155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0a24b52799fe9ff086050fb736272d305d36a0e","tid":1515473,"uid":273916,"like":0,"d